::Feline::

She looked at both bots and blushed.  She knew that Chordate was hers 
to have. But here was another bot to try to win over.  She swayed her 
hips and moved her tail as she walked over to him. She stretched her 
hand for the other bot to shake. "I'm very pleased to meet you. I'm 
Feline. And you are?" She smiled with her eyes as much as her face.  
She gave him a disarming look and a friendly smile.
